Aqua Teen Hunger Force + Water = Aqua Teen Hunger Force Z
Aqua Teen Hunger Force Z + Bono = Aqua Teen Hunger Force Bono
Aqua Teen Hunger Force Bono + Aqua Teen Hunger Force Z = Aqua Teen Hunger Force Bono Z

5 - Steam Powered Giraffe Kite: 
Rockstar + Rockstar = Rock Band
Rock Band + Steam = Steam Powered Giraffe
Steam Powered Giraffe + U2 = Steam Powered U2
Kite + Steam Powered U2 = Steam Powered Kite
Steam Powered Giraffe + Steam Powered Kite = Steam Powered Giraffe Kite

5 - Surfing The Sky: 
Steam + Surfer = Steamroller
Steamroller + Steamroller = Road
Road + U2 = Where the Streets Have No Name
Surfer + Where the Streets Have No Name = Surfing The Streets
Kite + Surfing The Streets = Surfing The Sky
